<sec id="sec2dot5-ijerph-16-02518" class="sec">
 <div class="title" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">2.5. Determination of Fluorescence Lifetime</div>
 <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">The fluorescence lifetime of quantum dots was fitted by formula (2), and the weighted-average fluorescence lifetime 
  <div class="inline-formula">
   <div id="mm2" class="math">
    <div class="mrow">
     <div class="mrow">
      <div class="msub">
       <span mathvariant="sans-serif" class="mi">τ</span>
       <div class="mrow">
        <span class="mi">av</span>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div> was calculated by formula (3):
  <div id="FD2-ijerph-16-02518" class="disp-formula">
   <span class="label">(2)</span>
   <div id="mm3" class="math">
    <div class="mrow">
     <div class="mrow">
      <span mathvariant="normal" class="mi">R</span>
      <span stretchy="false" class="mo">(</span>
      <span mathvariant="normal" class="mi">t</span>
      <span stretchy="false" class="mo">)</span>
      <span class="mo">=</span>
      <div class="msub">
       <span mathvariant="normal" class="mi">B</span>
       <span class="mn">1</span>
      </div>
      <div class="msup">
       <span mathvariant="normal" class="mi">e</span>
       <div class="mrow">
        <div class="mrow">
         <span stretchy="false" class="mo">(</span>
         <div class="mrow">
          <span class="mo">−</span>
          <div class="mfrac">
           <span mathvariant="normal" class="mi">t</span>
           <div class="mrow">
            <div class="msub">
             <span mathvariant="sans-serif" class="mi">τ</span>
             <span class="mn">1</span>
            </div>
           </div>
          </div>
         </div>
         <span stretchy="false" class="mo">)</span>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
      <span class="mo">+</span>
      <div class="msub">
       <span mathvariant="normal" class="mi">B</span>
       <span class="mn">2</span>
      </div>
      <div class="msup">
       <span mathvariant="normal" class="mi">e</span>
       <div class="mrow">
        <div class="mrow">
         <span stretchy="false" class="mo">(</span>
         <div class="mrow">
          <span class="mo">−</span>
          <div class="mfrac">
           <span mathvariant="normal" class="mi">t</span>
           <div class="mrow">
            <div class="msub">
             <span mathvariant="sans-serif" class="mi">τ</span>
             <span class="mn">2</span>
            </div>
           </div>
          </div>
         </div>
         <span stretchy="false" class="mo">)</span>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
      <span class="mtext"> </span>
     </div>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>
  <div id="FD3-ijerph-16-02518" class="disp-formula">
   <span class="label">(3)</span>
   <div id="mm4" class="math">
    <div class="mrow">
     <div class="mrow">
      <div class="msub">
       <span mathvariant="sans-serif" class="mi">τ</span>
       <div class="mrow">
        <span class="mi">av</span>
       </div>
      </div>
      <span class="mo">=</span>
      <div class="mfrac">
       <div class="mrow">
        <div mathsize="80%" displaystyle="true" class="mstyle">
         <span class="mo">∑</span>
        </div>
        <div class="msub">
         <span mathvariant="normal" class="mi">B</span>
         <span mathvariant="normal" class="mi">i</span>
        </div>
        <div class="msubsup">
         <span mathvariant="sans-serif" class="mi">τ</span>
         <span mathvariant="normal" class="mi">i</span>
         <span class="mn">2</span>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="mrow">
        <div mathsize="80%" displaystyle="true" class="mstyle">
         <span class="mo">∑</span>
        </div>
        <div class="msub">
         <span mathvariant="normal" class="mi">B</span>
         <span mathvariant="normal" class="mi">i</span>
        </div>
        <div class="msub">
         <span mathvariant="sans-serif" class="mi">τ</span>
         <span mathvariant="normal" class="mi">i</span>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
      <span class="mtext"> </span>
     </div>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div> where τ
  <sub>1</sub> and τ
  <sub>2</sub> represent time constants, and B
  <sub>1</sub> and B
  <sub>2</sub> represent the weight.
 </p>
